OOC:this will be my last post until Tuesday, Im going on yet another vacation!

:::Data and Defection landed in North America. What waited for them was a 
great orb that was flashing pictures, They put there hands to it and saw what 
Herald had seen so long ago:::

    a battle, Every spark on Earth was there, Mech fluid and bodies folded 
the valley. The many Factions fought senselessly. Defection was in the mid 
trying desperately to stop it all, DataStreaks body lay fallen and crumpled 
in the rising pool of mech. They looked to the sky and saw Countless angles 
Battling there was Heraldangle singing a song of peace that was nearly 
drowned out by the bloodlust cries of the innocent falling and the untruthful 
prevailing then an explosion, defection had sacrificed himself for Hot 
Rod.They saw Gigatron Fighting to get to defection and then seeing his corps. 
herald had just put himself in front of one of ArcAngles FireBalls saving 
Prowls life.ArcAngle, In all of his glory had lost someone close to him. then 
all were dead, the Iliad of the bots had ended in complete and utter death. 
Data Defection  and Herald Suddenly froze for 2 days.
